                    person best able to provide you assistant. A <strong style="color:#fff;">Astha Digital</strong> representative will
                    contact you shortly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="container-contact">
                <div class="contactInfo">
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i></div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h3>Address</h3>
                            <p>Gauhniya, Jasra,<br /> Prayagraj, Uttar Pradesh <br />INDIA - 212107
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-telephone"></i></div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h3>Phone</h3>
                            <p><a href="tel:919026297134>">+91 9026297134</a> <br> <a href="tel:919936762093">+91 9936762093</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-envelope-open"></i></div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h3>E-mail</h3>
                            <p><a href="mailto:info@asthadigital.co.in">info@asthadigital.co.in</a><br><a href="mailto:brikum1994@gmail.com">brikum1994@gmail.com</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-globe"></i></i></div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h3>Visit</h3>
